msgstr "Stirred by a cool breeze,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.22:5.4"
msgid ""
"Suttaṃ <span class=\"var\" title=\"jhānaṃ (s2, s3) | jhāyiṃ (?)\" id=\""
"note26\">jhāyaṃ</span> nibodhentī”ti."
msgstr "they wake the sleeper to practice absorption."

